Loading of many icons is quite slow. For daily usage, pretty interface is no so important as quick feedback from server is. Add possibility -- maybe in user profile -- to turn off displaying of icons for status, priority, type of issue and so on and to use for example letters instead of them ('B' -- bug, 'T' -- task, 'I' -- Improvement, 's' -- subtask, 'N' -- new feature). Loading and displaying of search results with many of issues or road map for project may be much faster.

